  "prompt": "Build a counter circuit with a 7-segment display (7 segment pins: 3-9) and a button on pin 2 with INPUT_PULLUP. The button needs proper wiring with GND on the opposite side. Include 220Ω resistor for segment current limiting and 10kΩ pull-up resistor.",
