          "type": "text",
          "text": "Good. Now I have the wiring rules. Let me plan the layout carefully:\n\n**Plan:**\n- **7-Segment Display**: pins a-g map to Arduino D3–D9, needs a 220Ω resistor in series (shared/common resistor on the common cathode path)\n- **Button**: one side → Arduino D2, opposite side → GND (INPUT_PULLUP)\n- **10kΩ pull-up resistor**: between D2 and 5V (hardware backup, though INPUT_PULLUP uses internal)\n- **220Ω resistor**: on the common cathode of the 7-segment display\n\nLet me place all components now:"
